---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const serviceTitle = 'Lead Capture + CRM Integrator';
const metadata = {
  title: `${serviceTitle} - Capybara Studios`,
  description: `Streamline your sales pipeline with our ${serviceTitle} service, ensuring no lead falls through the cracks.`,
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <header class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter font-heading dark:text-gray-200">
          {serviceTitle}
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-muted dark:text-slate-300">
          Automate lead capture, qualification, and CRM sync. Never miss a lead and keep your sales pipeline organized
          and responsive.
        </p>
      </header>

      <article class="prose dark:prose-invert lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            The Problem: Leaky Buckets and Lost Opportunities
          </h2>
          <p>
            Are valuable leads slipping through the cracks due to manual processes or disconnected systems? Many
            businesses struggle to efficiently capture, qualify, and route leads to their sales teams, resulting in
            missed opportunities and a disorganized pipeline. Common issues include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Manual data entry of leads from contact forms, emails, or social media into your CRM.</li>
            <li>Delayed follow-up times, allowing competitors to engage first.</li>
            <li>Inconsistent lead qualification processes.</li>
            <li>Difficulty tracking lead sources and measuring ROI on marketing efforts.</li>
            <li>Sales teams spending too much time on administrative tasks instead of selling.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            The Capybara Studios Way: Seamless Lead Management Automation
          </h2>
          <p>
            Our Lead Capture + CRM Integrator service provides a robust, automated system to ensure every lead is
            captured, nurtured, and managed effectively. We connect your various lead sources directly to your CRM,
            streamlining the entire process. Here's our approach:
          </p>
          <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3">
            <li>
              <strong>Omni-Channel Lead Source Integration:</strong> We connect all your lead generation points—website forms,
              landing pages, social media ads, email marketing, chatbots—to a central automation hub.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Automated Data Capture & Enrichment:</strong> Leads are automatically captured, and where possible,
              enriched with additional data (e.g., company information, social profiles) to provide a fuller picture for
              your sales team.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Intelligent Lead Qualification & Scoring:</strong> We can implement automated lead scoring based on
              predefined criteria (e.g., demographics, engagement, firmographics) to prioritize high-potential leads.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Instant CRM Synchronization:</strong> Qualified leads, along with all relevant data, are instantly
              and accurately synced to your CRM (e.g., HubSpot, Salesforce, Pipedrive, Notion), creating new deals or updating
              existing records.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Automated Notifications & Task Creation:</strong> Sales reps can be automatically notified of new hot
              leads, and tasks can be created in the CRM for prompt follow-up.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Basic Nurturing Sequences:</strong> We can set up initial automated email nurturing sequences to engage
              leads immediately after capture, providing value and keeping your brand top-of-mind.
            </li>
          </ol>
          <p class="mt-4">
            By automating these critical steps, we help you build a more efficient, responsive, and organized sales
            pipeline, ensuring you maximize every opportunity.
          </p>
        </section>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center py-8 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            Ready to Supercharge Your Sales Pipeline?
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-6 text-muted dark:text-slate-300">
            Stop losing leads and start closing more deals with automated efficiency.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-3">Automate Your Lead Flow</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

